{"tid":1848071,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老母話香港人要返黎香港所以唔封得關","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T10:04:39.000Z","uid":103842,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d278fa185e0d2669efd5d8098597322ea21bf41f","tid":1848071,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"咁你剩係俾有香港身份證既人入黎咪得囉<br />\n有香港身份證就有入無出 無證既有出無入<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲話特首WO? 屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"eb8e23e12887fcc64c10dae0495844b67f69f8a1","tid":1848071,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要求所有口岸（包括機場、羅湖、落馬洲、深圳灣、港珠澳大橋）全面禁止來自中國大陸旅客入境香港，否則繼續三罷！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">備注：<br />\n1.）非中國大陸旅客（包括台灣）可以正常入境香港<br />\n2.）擁有香港永久性居民身分可以正常入境香港<br />\n3.）香港永久性居民及其他國藉旅客經中國大陸入境香港必須接受為期14日隔離及醫學監察</span>"},{"pid":"a30b6c966891481ec4cbc9aa28eed5b4ef52a411","tid":1848071,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"仲有好多支那曱甴都有香港身份證"},{"pid":"0ad084027ec130079aa4e975f81d4c67c1ef79a4","tid":1848071,"uid":39470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:51:29.000Z","msg":"因為戴避孕套唔係100%安全，所以唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411ac61ea9b383ff6a815c37dee2b4e1a59ffd11","tid":1848071,"uid":217450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:51:34.000Z","msg":"其實咁簡單嘅嘢&hellip;佢點會諗唔到<br />\n扮明係有心"},{"pid":"dfb93ed13e04a9877d6532d48f87f43bcccbeaeb","tid":1848071,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"核彈: 有香港人無香港身份證"},{"pid":"12de94b0a3c1df39e757022d8e12666fb647bc89","tid":1848071,"uid":73863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:53:48.000Z","msg":"佢呢啲係混淆試聽，想令其他藍絲覺得一封就